    <!-- OUR MISSION -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="intro-heading">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-label">Our Mission</span>
          <h2 id="intro-heading">Cognitive decline affects millions of families. We exist to help.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content-width">
          <p class="lead">
            More than 55 million people worldwide live with dementia, and millions more serve as their caregivers. These families deserve better research, better tools, and better support.
          </p>
          <p class="lead">
            We fund and conduct research into cognitive decline. We explore technology that helps families manage day-to-day challenges. And we collect real stories from caregivers and families to inform everything we build.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


